TITLE: Defining RBAC Policy in Rego for Express.js API Endpoint
DESCRIPTION: This Rego code defines an authorization policy for the '/api/protected' endpoint. It allows access only to users with the 'admin' role by checking the user's roles array in the input object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/aserto-dev/aserto-docs/blob/main/docs/quickstarts/react/create-a-policy.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: rego
CODE:
```
package asertodemo.GET.api.protected

default allowed = false

allowed {
	some index
	input.user.properties.roles[index] == "admin"
}
```

