TITLE: Configuring Decision Logger for Edge Authorizer in YAML
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for setting up the decision logger on an Edge Authorizer. Specifies the store directory for buffering logs, scribe connection details including certificates, and shipper parameters. Used to enable resilient decision logging with persistent storage.
